name: BlackPink Jisoo Jennie Lisa Rosé Dress Up Game
name_original: BlackPink Jisoo Jennie Lisa Rosé Dress Up Game
description:
Blackpink members Jisoo, Jennie, Lisa and Rosé are getting ready for the concert. They're trying on their new costumes. Let's choose the most beautiful skirts, trousers, socks, shoes, jewelry and bags and dress them.

Tap the screen to play.
